QuestData.Title: Burn Them Down
QuestData.Description: Now, we begin our assault, $n!$b$bGet down to Agurak's Fall and use these tarbombs to destroy their rylak egg incubators.$b$bWhile you are busy I will sneak down into their camp and prepare for the next phase of our attack. Meet me there once you have burned everything.
QuestData.LogDescription: Burn down the Thunderlord Rylak Incubators within Agurak's Fall.
